{"tid":2147671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐西蘭一百日零本地個案啊,香港呢啲垃圾地方算鳩數啦","createTime":"2020-08-09T11:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T08:51:07.000Z","uid":237459,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"40d994d97e5bf8a299ad0f3e33354529e9414f80","tid":2147671,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200809/4J6VVYPK7ZGCH3TB65B45M3YHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200809%2F4J6VVYPK7ZGCH3TB65B45M3YHU%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=cdce60dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200809%2F4J6VVYPK7ZGCH3TB65B45M3YHU%2F&h=2b1508df\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200809/4J6VVYPK7ZGCH3TB65B45M3YHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭今（9日）則滿100天無本土病例。人口500萬的紐西蘭，自3月19日起封關，5月1日通報最後一起本土病例，累計確診病例為1219起。目前紐西蘭人生活如常，沒有社交距離等措施，體育、文化活動也照常進行，但邊境仍實施嚴格限制，入境者須隔離14天。"},{"pid":"35a287ec4294479bff78143514c388b3fb8dfe3d","tid":2147671,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1d486e526642ca724a3856122325e617b380a2","tid":2147671,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a5e38571c4fc146637c81f54be83dc6f92bc7b","tid":2147671,"uid":365024,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"連燈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNew Zealand has four confirmed cases of COVID-19 in one family acquired from an unknown source.<br />\n<br />\nThe index case is a person in their 50s who lives in South Auckland.​<br />\n​<br />\nThey were swabbed yesterday, and the swab was processed twice. A second swab has been taken today confirms the positive result.​<br />\n​<br />\nThe person has been symptomatic for five days and has been interviewed by Auckland Regional Public Health. The person has no overseas travel history.​<br />\n​<br />\nAs is our usual protocol we have traced and continue to trace close and casual contacts of this person and getting them tested for COVID-19.​<br />\n​<br />\nThis has included household contacts of the case who received a rapid test this evening. Three of these tests have also come back positive and we are awaiting three further results.​<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/183410325126292/posts/2062198100580829/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F183410325126292%2Fposts%2F2062198100580829%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=00c30668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/183410325126292/posts/2062198100580829/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"cfb45e4c8781302872dccc8ae0fa27a4c970a220","tid":2147671,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c78e8baf90305d5e0fe6541fe3f1b28156fbbe","tid":2147671,"uid":50737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"特首唔同"},{"pid":"429d6279a3bc370777b1374ab8d3fa56f370ac9a","tid":2147671,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dis